<section class="section ai-without-specs" id="ai-without-specs">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="section-header">
			<h2>Don't Be a Vibe Coder</h2>
			<p class="section-subtitle">
				AI can generate code fast, but without proper planning, you're building on quicksand. Real software engineering is needed now more than ever.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="comparison-grid">
			<div class="comparison-pair">
				<div class="comparison-card without">
					<div class="card-header">
						<span class="card-icon">
							<svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
								<path d="M12 2 2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"></path>
								<path d="m2 17 10 5 10-5"></path>
								<path d="m2 12 10 5 10-5"></path>
								<line x1="6" y1="10" x2="6" y2="14"></line>
								<line x1="18" y1="10" x2="18" y2="14"></line>
							</svg>
						</span>
						<span class="card-badge danger">Without Specs</span>
					</div>
					<h3>Works On My Machine™</h3>
					<p>AI generates code that runs fine locally but falls apart at scale. Don't be misled by the latest "vibe coding" trend, businesses push it without a clue about real engineering.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="comparison-card with">
					<div class="card-header">
						<span class="card-icon">
							<svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
								<path d="M12 2 2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"></path>
								<path d="m2 17 10 5 10-5"></path>
								<path d="m2 12 10 5 10-5"></path>
							</svg>
						</span>
						<span class="card-badge success">With Specs</span>
					</div>
					<h3>Built to Scale</h3>
					<p>Specs define performance requirements, load expectations, and scaling constraints upfront. AI builds systems that work in production, not just in demos.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="comparison-pair">
				<div class="comparison-card without">
					<div class="card-header">
						<span class="card-icon">
							<svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
								<path d="M21.5 2v6h-6M2.5 22v-6h6M2 11.5a10 10 0 0 1 18.8-4.3M22 12.5a10 10 0 0 1-18.8 4.2"></path>
							</svg>
						</span>
						<span class="card-badge danger">Without Specs</span>
					</div>
					<h3>Quick & Easy = Quick to Fail</h3>
					<p>Users hate rushed apps. If building quality software in 2 months was <em>really</em> that easy, everyone would be doing it. Shortcuts show.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="comparison-card with">
					<div class="card-header">
						<span class="card-icon">
							<svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
								<polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
							</svg>
						</span>
						<span class="card-badge success">With Specs</span>
					</div>
					<h3>Built to Last</h3>
					<p>Thoughtful planning creates apps users love. Specs ensure quality requirements, user experience standards, and maintainability from day one.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="comparison-pair">
				<div class="comparison-card without">
					<div class="card-header">
						<span class="card-icon">
							<svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
								<circle cx="12" cy="12" r="1"></circle>
								<circle cx="19" cy="12" r="1"></circle>
								<circle cx="5" cy="12" r="1"></circle>
								<circle cx="12" cy="5" r="1"></circle>
								<circle cx="12" cy="19" r="1"></circle>
								<circle cx="5" cy="5" r="1"></circle>
								<circle cx="19" cy="5" r="1"></circle>
								<circle cx="5" cy="19" r="1"></circle>
								<circle cx="19" cy="19" r="1"></circle>
							</svg>
						</span>
						<span class="card-badge danger">Without Specs</span>
					</div>
					<h3>Ignores CS Fundamentals</h3>
					<p>Computer science principles get skipped, nested loops in O(n³), memory leaks, inefficient algorithms. AI doesn't optimize what you don't specify.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="comparison-card with">
					<div class="card-header">
						<span class="card-icon">
							<svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
								<path d="M5 12h14"></path>
								<path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path>
							</svg>
						</span>
						<span class="card-badge success">With Specs</span>
					</div>
					<h3>Applies CS Principles</h3>
					<p>Specs guide AI on Big-O complexity, data structures, and algorithms. Prompt for O(log n) search? AI delivers. Know what to ask for.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="comparison-pair">
				<div class="comparison-card without">
					<div class="card-header">
						<span class="card-icon">
							<svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
								<path d="m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3Z"></path>
								<path d="M12 9v4"></path>
								<path d="M12 17h.01"></path>
							</svg>
						</span>
						<span class="card-badge danger">Without Specs</span>
					</div>
					<h3>Security Afterthought</h3>
					<p>SQL injection, XSS, exposed secrets, weak authentication, security gets bolted on too late. Production breaches waiting to happen.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="comparison-card with">
					<div class="card-header">
						<span class="card-icon">
							<svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
								<path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"></path>
								<path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"></path>
							</svg>
						</span>
						<span class="card-badge success">With Specs</span>
					</div>
					<h3>Security by Design</h3>
					<p>Requirements include threat models, auth flows, data validation, and encryption standards. AI implements OWASP best practices from the start.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="callout">
			<h4>Bottom Line</h4>
			<p>AI is a multiplier, not a replacement for thinking. Give it clear specs, and it becomes your most productive teammate.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.ai-without-specs {
		background: var(--color-pastel-blue);
	}

	.section-header {
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
		max-width: 900px;
		margin-left: auto;
		margin-right: auto;
	}

	.section-subtitle {
		font-size: var(--text-xl);
		color: var(--color-text-secondary);
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin-top: var(--space-4);
	}

	.comparison-grid {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: var(--space-12);
		margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
	}

	.comparison-pair {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: var(--space-8);
	}

	.comparison-card {
		background: var(--color-white);
		border: var(--border-width) solid var(--color-border);
		border-radius: var(--border-radius);
		padding: var(--space-8);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-brutal-sm);
		transition: all var(--transition-fast);
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
	}

	.comparison-card:hover {
		transform: translate(2px, 2px);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-brutal);
	}

	.comparison-card.without {
		background: var(--color-pastel-pink);
	}

	.comparison-card.with {
		background: var(--color-pastel-green);
	}

	.card-header {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: space-between;
		margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
	}

	.card-icon {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		color: var(--color-gray-900);
	}

	.card-icon svg {
		stroke-width: 2.5;
	}

	.card-badge {
		font-size: var(--text-xs);
		font-weight: 700;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
		padding: var(--space-1) var(--space-3);
		border-radius: 100px;
		border: 2px solid var(--color-border);
	}

	.card-badge.danger {
		background: var(--color-danger);
		color: white;
	}

	.card-badge.success {
		background: var(--color-success);
		color: white;
	}

	.comparison-card h3 {
		font-size: var(--text-2xl);
		margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
		color: var(--color-gray-900);
		font-weight: 800;
	}

	.comparison-card p {
		font-size: var(--text-lg);
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: var(--color-text-secondary);
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}

	.callout {
		background: var(--color-white);
		padding: var(--space-10);
		border-radius: var(--border-radius);
		border: var(--border-width) solid var(--color-border);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-brutal);
		text-align: center;
	}

	.callout h4 {
		font-size: var(--text-2xl);
		margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
		color: var(--color-gray-900);
	}

	.callout p {
		font-size: var(--text-xl);
		margin-bottom: 0;
		max-width: 700px;
		margin-left: auto;
		margin-right: auto;
		color: var(--color-gray-900);
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	/* Responsive */
	@media (max-width: 968px) {
		.comparison-pair {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: var(--space-6);
		}
	}
</style>
